{"tid":2040948,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"何君堯建議抽起教育撥款資助海洋公園營運","createTime":"2020-05-29T02:25:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T04:31:31.000Z","uid":21470,"like":6,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"8bbe44add597630e4f4bb5ea3aa8075928502f57","tid":2040948,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:25:28.000Z","msg":"何君堯建議抽起教育撥款資助海洋公園營運<br />\n29.05.2020 10:00<br />\n<br />\n財委會繼續審議海洋公園54億元撥款申請，何君堯認為本港教育已經腐敗，建議政府抽起政府向教育的撥款，用作資助海洋公園，同時將公園的機動遊戲全部搬過迪士尼樂園合併，全力將海洋公園打造成國際品牌。民主黨林卓廷認為不可行，指迪士尼本身有機動遊戲，要拆卸及搬遷機動遊戲亦要成本。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨胡志偉指，公園日後可能會因應發展需要改變土地用途，會否改成房屋等用途，商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華回應指暫時未有考慮。建築、測量及都市規劃界功能界別議員謝偉銓認為，公園部分用地可產生商業效益，可以補貼園方收入。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293231&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1293231%26csid%3D261_341&d=hmvw4%2FD%2BM9RG0cIfJpNLuwhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=1fdf46d0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1293231&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"ca729f309755f6a6bc14df8d6c85d01a6e9a9c4b","tid":2040948,"uid":188176,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"應該係地球上首例抽起教育既錢去起公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce5aa3e1abd513d67254b1d1481f53061c464c7","tid":2040948,"uid":148817,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"ca729f309755f6a6bc14df8d6c85d01a6e9a9c4b","tid":2040948,"uid":188176,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:26:50.000Z","msg":"應該係地球上首例抽起教育既錢去起公園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-29T02:27:31.000Z","msg":"真係智障<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />